ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Export Control List
PrecisOrder Amending the EXPORT CONTROL LIST in order to (1) reflect the Government of Canada's obligations, commitments and Policies resulting from Canada's participation in the Wassenaar Arrangement on Export Controls for Conventional Arms and Dual-Use Goods and Technologies, the Nuclear Suppliers Group, the Missile Technology Control Regime and the Australia Group; and (2) remove controls that are determined to no longer be necessary.
